data.description: Welcome to this stunning split floor plan home that is full of love and character. Located on a corner lot, this house provides that extra privacy on the south side. You will be greeted with a warm interior that allows for one to feel right at home. To go along with the warm interior, the cozy exterior features a covered patio perfect for entertaining. In this home you will find comfort and serenity from any area. This home is sure to catch your eye, schedule your showing today!
